snippet.title: Street Power Soccer - Reveal Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Throw it down and bring your best – street style soccer arrives on PlayStation 4 this summer! Learn more:http://streetpowergame.com

Sick style and high-energy action come together in this completely over-the-top soccer experience with Street legend Sean Garnier. Featuring six distinct game modes from open-ended Freestyle and Trick Shot modes to head-to-head competition in Panna and up to 3v3 matches in Street Power mode, you’ve never played soccer quite like this.

Learn more: http://streetpowergame.com
